@baseUrl = http://localhost:5050
@passengerToken = <paste_passenger_jwt_here>
@adminToken = <paste_admin_jwt_here>

### ── Passenger ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Create a support ticket
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/public/support-tickets
Authorization: Bearer {{passengerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rideId": "<ride-id>",
  "subject": "Incorrect charge",
  "description": "I was charged more than the estimated price shown before booking.",
  "priority": "High"
}

### Get own tickets
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/public/support-tickets
Authorization: Bearer {{passengerToken}}

### ── Admin ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### List all tickets
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/support-tickets?page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Get single ticket
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/support-tickets/<ticket-id>
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Update ticket status and admin notes
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/support-tickets/<ticket-id>
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "InProgress",
  "adminNotes": "Investigating the pricing logs for this ride."
}

### Resolve a ticket
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/support-tickets/<ticket-id>
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "Resolved",
  "adminNotes": "Confirmed overcharge — refund of €5 issued."
}
